Subject: [PATCH 041/129] kernel: LS1021AIOT support

Upstream-Status: Pending

* Add defconfig/dts/driver_fix for LS1021AIOT;
* Add ThinkEco dongle's pid & vid;

Signed-off-by: Miao Xiaowei <B49897@freescale.com>
[Xulin: Original patch taken from
Freescale-Linux-SDK-for-LS1021A-IOT-Rev2-v0.4-SOURCE-20150907-yocto.iso]
Signed-off-by: Xulin Sun <xulin.sun@windriver.com>
---
